genresAdvancedInfo.name: musica eletronica gospel
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre of electronic music combines gospel lyrics and themes with electronic beats and sounds. It is often used in Christian worship services and features uplifting and inspirational lyrics set to danceable rhythms. It is a popular genre in Brazil and other Latin American countries.
